thread.title: KEN MOELLER
thread.title_full: Maine Lobster Now reviewed by KEN MOELLER

author: KEN MOELLER
title: KEN MOELLER
text: This is the second time that I have order from Maine Lobster Now. I have been very pleased with their service and would recommend ordering without any worry. Both shipments were delivered to South Carolina and arrived on schedule and in excellent shape - live lobsters and clams for family members to enjoy. I hope this has been helpful in making your decision to order from Maine Lobster Now.
